Instructions for Lynis

#Getting lynis off of github
cd /(directory of choosing)
git clone https://github.com/CISOfy/lynis

#Running lynis
#Must be in the directory of download
cd lynis
lynis audit system

#Logs, logs are purged before every run
default log location is: /var/log/lynis.log

#Reports
default report location is: /var/log/lynis-report.dat
